<div class="col-xs-12">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="text-center">Local OAuth2</h1>
  </div>
  <p>
    This is a "robust enough" OAuth2 API for local development. It doesn't
    support all things OAuth2.
  </p>

  <h3>Code authorization</h3>
  <pre><%= auth_url %></pre>
  <h3>cURL</h3>
  <h6>Endpoint request</h6>
  <pre>curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= access_token %>" <%= url %></pre>
</div>
